            </ConnectedComponents>
            <Execution>
                - Stateless conversions using cell size and origin assumptions.
            </Execution>
            <Timing>
                - On-demand.
            </Timing>
            <Invariants>
                - Maze dimension is fixed to 4 rows, 8 columns.
                - Start cell coordinate remains constant.
